summary: Custom dungeon for Skyrim, an ancient ruin located south of Helgen, on a road that leads to Southfringe Sanctum.
descriptionHtml:
Hi everybody. This is my third Skyrim dungeon mod. Here is a short description:

-It is an ancient ruin located south of Helgen, on a road that leads to Southfringe Sanctum.

-It is of medium difficulty, suitable for characters of Level 15 and above.

-It is half the length of my previous dungeon (Windcaller's Pass) and it provides around 15 minutes of gameplay.


Feel free to rate and comment. As always, I am interested to know if this map feels like something that could have been created by Bethesda's design team for the original Skyrim. Thanks.

This map has been cleaned with 'TES5 Edit' tool. But if you experience any bugs, crashes, odd loading times or any similar problems, please let me know.

NOTE: This dungeon has also been included in The Legacy of the Dragonborn mod.

NOTE: If you liked this dungeon mod, feel free to check out my other 2 dungeons:
-Ogmund's Tomb.
-Windcaller's Pass.
author: Predrag Pesic
